-punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\">,</span> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">65</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">                <span class=\"hljs-attr\">&quot;version&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;0&quot;</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">66</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">            <span class=\"hljs-punctuation\">}</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">67</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">        <span class=\"hljs-punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\">,</span> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">68</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">        <span class=\"hljs-attr\">&quot;sequence&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;2&quot;</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">69</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-punctuation\">}</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">70</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\">}</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>一个通道配置块类似上面这种,为了看的清楚有些内容我删了, 更换证书我们需要保证application及orderer的MSP是相同的, 否则更新配置块是不会成功的, 且我们得保证当前组织的raft节点的证书也要全部更换掉.</p>\n<h2 id=\"失败过程\">失败过程</h2>\n","bodyMarkdown":"","bodyHtml":"","rawMarkdown":"","plainText":"","toc":[],"slugForSearch":"afc6d6dd","comments":true,"math":false,"mermaid":false},{"kind":"post","sourcePath":"source/_posts/使用GVT-g显卡虚拟化.md","route":"/posts/3a1d136/","abbrlink":"3a1d136","title":"使用GVT-g显卡虚拟化","date":"2021-01-17 20:53:29","updated":"2021-01-17 20:53:29","tags":["Linux","qemu","GVT-g","intel"],"categories":["Linux"],"language":"zh-Hans","htmlLang":"zh-Hans","locale":"zh_CN","textDirection":"ltr","dateLocale":"zh-CN","excerptMarkdown":"","excerptHtml":"<h2 id=\"为内核添加参数\">为内核添加参数</h2>\n<p>比如<code>grub</code>在<code>/etc/default/grub</code>的<code>GRUB_CMDLINE_LINUX_DEFAULT=</code>中添加</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-ini\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-attr\">intel_iommu</span>=<span class=\"hljs-literal\">on</span> i915.enable_gvt=<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span> i915.enable_guc=<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"启用modules\">启用modules</h2>\n<p>在<code>/etc/mkinitcpio.conf</code>的MODULES=()`中添加:</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-ini\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\"># linux 5.14后，arch的linux内核模块已经不会勾选vfio-mdev，自测不影响gvt-g</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">kvmgt vfio vfio-iommu-type1s</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>然后运行,我用的zen内核所以是linux-zen,默认内核是linux</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-built_in\">sudo</span> mkinitcpio -p linux-zen</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>重启计算机</p>\n<p>查看<code>/sys/devices/pci0000:00/0000:00:02.0/mdev_supported_types</code>可以看见类似如下的目录</p>\n","bodyMarkdown":"","bodyHtml":"","rawMarkdown":"","plainText":"","toc":[],"slugForSearch":"3a1d136","comments":true,"math":false,"mermaid":false},{"kind":"post","sourcePath":"source/_posts/gpg使用.md","route":"/posts/7d547224/","abbrlink":"7d547224","title":"gpg使用","date":"2020-10-02 14:00:01","updated":"2020-10-02 14:00:01","tags":["linux","encrypt"],"categories":["linux"],"language":"zh-Hans","htmlLang":"zh-Hans","locale":"zh_CN","textDirection":"ltr","dateLocale":"zh-CN","excerptMarkdown":"","excerptHtml":"<p>生成一个密钥</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">gpg --full-gen-key</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>之后会选择加密方式, 有效期, 用户名及邮箱, 密码, 按自己需求填就行了.</p>\n<p>创建一个子密钥</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">gpg --edit-key [key <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">hash</span>]</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">gpg&gt; addkey</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">#只有与前面是相同的, 按需求选择.</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">6</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">gpg&gt; save</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">7</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\"># 保存</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>导出密钥</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">gpg -o /path/gpg_key --export-secret-keys [key <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">hash</span>]</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>导出子密钥</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">gpg -o /path/gpg_key.sub --export-secret-subkeys [key <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">hash</span>]</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>导出吊销证书</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">gpg --generate-revocation [key <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">hash</span>]</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\"># 输出是文本内容, 复制保存下来就行了</span></span></span></code></pre>\n","bodyMarkdown":"","bodyHtml":"","rawMarkdown":"","plainText":"","toc":[],"slugForSearch":"7d547224","comments":true,"math":false,"mermaid":false},{"kind":"post","sourcePath":"source/_posts/GeoIP-mmdb-format.md","route":"/posts/931c13a4/","abbrlink":"931c13a4","title":"GeoIP mmdb format","date":"2020-07-27 22:15:17","updated":"2020-07-27 22:15:17","tags":["Network"],"categories":["Network"],"language":"en","htmlLang":"en","locale":"en_US","textDirection":"ltr","dateLocale":"en-US","excerptMarkdown":"","excerptHtml":"<p>complete document <a href=\"https://maxmind.github.io/MaxMind-DB/\">MaxMind DB File Format SpecificationDescription</a></p>\n<p>here is only how convert trie tree to array</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-markdown\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">0100, 1011 -&gt; trie</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-code\">              root</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-code\">               |</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-code\">         +-----+------+</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">6</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-code\">        /              \\</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">7</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-code\">       0                1</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">8</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-code\">     /   \\             /  \\</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">9</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-code\">   null   1           0   null</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">10</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-code\">         / \\        /   \\</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">11</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-code\">        0 null     null   1</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">12</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-code\">       / \\               / \\</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">13</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-code\">       0 null         null  1</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">14</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-code\"></span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>trie -&gt; array<br>\nleft is 0, right is 1<br>\nvalue is index of array</p>\n","bodyMarkdown":"","bodyHtml":"","rawMarkdown":"","plainText":"","toc":[],"slugForSearch":"931c13a4","comments":true,"math":false,"mermaid":false},{"kind":"post","sourcePath":"source/_posts/DNS-over-HTTPS.md","route":"/posts/4b39445f/","abbrlink":"4b39445f","title":"DNS over HTTPS","date":"2020-06-23 00:30:08","updated":"2020-06-23 00:30:08","tags":["DNS","DOH","golang"],"categories":["Network"],"language":"zh-Hans","htmlLang":"zh-Hans","locale":"zh_CN","textDirection":"ltr","dateLocale":"zh-CN","excerptMarkdown":"","excerptHtml":"<p>这个DNS系列现在有以下几篇文章<br>\n<a href=\"/posts/f05986bf/\">DNS</a>  <a href=\"/posts/668530ca/\">EDNS</a> <a href=\"/posts/1751943e/\">DNSSEC</a> <a href=\"/posts/4b39445f/\">DNS over HTTPS</a> 完整代码请看<a href=\"https://github.com/Asutorufa/yuhaiin/tree/master/net/dns\">DNS</a></p>\n<hr>\n<p>DOH就比较简单了,因为DOH使用的请求数据和应答数据均为之前的DNS协议格式,包括DNS,EDNS,DNSSEC…当然是否支持EDNS,DNSSEC需要看DNS服务器的支持情况<br>\nDOH的最主要的区别是把DNS使用的UDP,换成了HTTPS,这样就能防止DNS污染了,而且可以使用DNSSEC加上ESNI来防止证书劫持,DOH的协议在<a href=\"https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc8484\">rfc8484</a>中有定义<br>\nDOH主要有两种方式HTTP的GET请求和POST的请求</p>\n<h2 id=\"get\">GET</h2>\n<p>GET请求需要使用BASE64对请求的字节数据进行序列化,然后作为参数传递,获取到的数据使用我们之前的解析进行解析就行了</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-go\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">func</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">get</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">(dReq []<span class=\"hljs-type\">byte</span>, server <span class=\"hljs-type\">string</span>)</span></span> (body []<span class=\"hljs-type\">byte</span>, err <span class=\"hljs-type\">error</span>) {</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> query := strings.Replace(base64.URLEncoding.EncodeToString(dReq), <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;=&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">-1</span>)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> urls := <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;https://&quot;</span> + server + <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;/dns-query?dns=&quot;</span> + query</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> res, err := http.Get(urls)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> err != <span class=\"hljs-literal\">nil</span> {</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">6</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"hljs-literal\">nil</span>, err</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">7</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> }</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">8</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">defer</span> res.Body.Close()</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">9</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> body, err = ioutil.ReadAll(res.Body)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">10</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> err != <span class=\"hljs-literal\">nil</span> {</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">11</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"hljs-literal\">nil</span>, err</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">12</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> }</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">13</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">14</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">}</span></span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"post\">POST</h2>\n<p>POST并不需要进行序列化,直接把原始请求数据作为body就行了</p>\n","bodyMarkdown":"","bodyHtml":"","rawMarkdown":"","plainText":"","toc":[],"slugForSearch":"4b39445f","comments":true,"math":false,"mermaid":false},{"kind":"post","sourcePath":"source/_posts/DNSSEC.md","route":"/posts/1751943e/","abbrlink":"1751943e","title":"DNSSEC","date":"2020-06-23 00:21:33","updated":"2020-06-23 00:21:33","tags":["DNS","UDP","DNSSEC","golang"],"categories":["Network"],"language":"zh-Hans","htmlLang":"zh-Hans","locale":"zh_CN","textDirection":"ltr","dateLocale":"zh-CN","excerptMarkdown":"","excerptHtml":"<p>这个DNS系列现在有以下几篇文章<br>\n<a href=\"/posts/f05986bf/\">DNS</a>  <a href=\"/posts/668530ca/\">EDNS</a> <a href=\"/posts/1751943e/\">DNSSEC</a> <a href=\"/posts/4b39445f/\">DNS over HTTPS</a> 完整代码请看<a href=\"https://github.com/Asutorufa/yuhaiin/tree/master/net/dns\">DNS</a></p>\n<hr>\n<p>注意: 这里我只完成了请求字段,主要原因是因为我学习这些DNS协议是为了找到防止DNS污染的方法,而DNSSEC并不能,而且应答头比较复杂,可能还要了解ssl和tls的知识,所以这里我没有完成代码,想了解的请看<a href=\"https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc3225\">protocol change</a> <a href=\"https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc4034\">rfc4034</a> <a href=\"https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc4035\">rfc4035</a> <a href=\"https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc4034#appendix-A.1\">Algorithm</a></p>\n<p>DNSSEC也是使用了EDNS,而且只需要改一个字段,就是之前提到Z,具体协议请看</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-markdown\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-code\">                +0 (MSB)                +1 (LSB)</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-code\">         +--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-code\">      0: |   EXTENDED-RCODE      |       VERSION         |</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-code\">         +--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-code\">      2: |DO|                    Z                       |</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">6</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-code\">         +--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">7</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-code\"></span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>完成请求头</p>\n","bodyMarkdown":"","bodyHtml":"","rawMarkdown":"","plainText":"","toc":[],"slugForSearch":"1751943e","comments":true,"math":false,"mermaid":false},{"kind":"post","sourcePath":"source/_posts/EDNS.md","route":"/posts/668530ca/","abbrlink":"668530ca","title":"EDNS","date":"2020-06-22 23:09:49","updated":"2020-06-22 23:09:49","tags":["DNS","UDP","EDNS","golang"],"categories":["Network"],"language":"zh-Hans","htmlLang":"zh-Hans","locale":"zh_CN","textDirection":"ltr","dateLocale":"zh-CN","excerptMarkdown":"","excerptHtml":"<p>这个DNS系列现在有以下几篇文章<br>\n<a href=\"/posts/f05986bf/\">DNS</a>  <a href=\"/posts/668530ca/\">EDNS</a> <a href=\"/posts/1751943e/\">DNSSEC</a> <a href=\"/posts/4b39445f/\">DNS over HTTPS</a> 完整代码请看<a href=\"https://github.com/Asutorufa/yuhaiin/tree/master/net/dns\">DNS</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"edns\">EDNS</h2>\n<p>上一篇我们写了DNS,EDNS就是DNS的功能扩充.<br>\n上一篇的DNS里头部有ARCOUNT的计数,EDNS就包含在那个里面,EDNS发送的请求在请求头之后的Additional中,应答在Answer和Authoritative之后,我们可看以下图,跟清晰了吧</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-markdown\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-code\">    +---------------------+</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-code\">    |        Header       |</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-code\">    +---------------------+</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-code\">    |       Question      | the question for the name server</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-code\">    +---------------------+</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">6</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-code\">    |        Answer       | RRs answering the question</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">7</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-code\">    +---------------------+</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">8</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-code\">    |      Authority      | RRs pointing toward an authority</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">9</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-code\">    +---------------------+</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">10</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-code\">    |      Additional     | RRs holding additional information</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">11</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-code\">    +---------------------+</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">12</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-code\"></span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"协议格式\">协议格式</h2>\n<p>具体协议内容请看<a href=\"https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc2671\">rfc2671</a>,<a href=\"https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc7871\">rfc7871</a></p>\n","bodyMarkdown":"","bodyHtml":"","rawMarkdown":"","plainText":"","toc":[],"slugForSearch":"668530ca","comments":true,"math":false,"mermaid":false}]}